OL,3,CNottinghamshire Police removed from
OL,4,Cenhanced monitoring by watchdog
OL,6,FNottinghamshire Police has made
OL,7,Fimprovements and has been removed from
OL,8,Fan enhanced level of monitoring by a
OL,9,Fwatchdog, after being put into special
OL,10,Fmeasures last year.
OL,12,FLast March, the East Midlands force
OL,13,Fwas told to "urgently produce an
OL,14,Fimprovement plan" by His Majesty's
OL,15,FInspectorate of Constabulary and Fire
OL,16,Fand Rescue Services (HMICFRS) after
OL,17,Fbeing put into special measures.
