OL,3,CNottinghamshire Police removed from
OL,4,Cenhanced monitoring by watchdog
OL,6,FThe report came after the force was
OL,7,Fcriticised for the way it handled of
OL,8,Fthe deaths of Grace O'Malley-Kumar,
OL,9,FBarnaby Webber, and Ian Coates, who
OL,10,Fwere killed by Valdo Calocane in
OL,11,FNottingham in 2023.
OL,13,FWhile the watchdog said the decision
OL,14,Fwas not linked to the force's handling
OL,15,Fof the case, the news was nevertheless
OL,16,Fwelcomed by relatives of Calocane's
OL,17,Fvictims as a sign that inspectors
OL,18,Frecognised how the force needed
OL,19,F"intervention and urgent improvement".
