OL,3,CNottinghamshire Police removed from
OL,4,Cenhanced monitoring by watchdog
OL,6,FThe report last year ranked three of
OL,7,Fthe eight areas of policing
OL,8,F"inadequate" in the review following
OL,9,Fan inspection from the end of 2023 to
OL,10,FJanuary.
OL,12,FForces are moved into special measures
OL,13,F` which HMICFRS calls being subjected
OL,14,Fto an "enhanced level of monitoring"
OL,15,Funder what is known as the "engage"
OL,16,Fprocess ` when they are not responding
OL,17,Fto concerns raised by the watchdog or
OL,18,Fare not "managing, mitigating or
OL,19,Feradicating these concerns".
