OL,3,CNottinghamshire Police removed from
OL,4,Cenhanced monitoring by watchdog
OL,6,FThe chief officer team was visible and
OL,7,Faccessible, and inspectors found a
OL,8,Fpositive culture and active
OL,9,Fparticipation in change across the
OL,10,Fworkforce; and the way it is
OL,11,Fpreventing and deterring crime, by
OL,12,Faddressing the issue of neighbourhood
OL,13,Fofficers and staff being unable to
OL,14,Fspend enough time working in their
OL,15,Fcommunities.
OL,17,FHM Inspector Roy Wilsher said:
