OL,3,CNottinghamshire Police removed from
OL,4,Cenhanced monitoring by watchdog
OL,6,F"I am pleased with the good progress
OL,7,Fthat Nottinghamshire Police has made
OL,8,Fso far. While there is still work to
OL,9,Fdo, I have recommended removing the
OL,10,Fservice from our enhanced level of
OL,11,Fmonitoring, known as engage, and
OL,12,Freturn it to routine monitoring.
OL,14,FHe went on to say:
OL,16,F"We are reassured by the plans the
OL,17,Fpolice force has in place to continue
OL,18,Fmaking improvements, particularly in
OL,19,Frelation to crime investigation,
OL,20,Fleadership, force management and
OL,21,Fneighbourhood policing.
