OL,6,F"We will continue to assess its
OL,7,Fprogress to make sure the people of
OL,8,FNottinghamshire are getting the
OL,9,Fservice they deserve."
OL,11,FCalocane was sentenced to an
OL,12,Findefinite hospital order last year
OL,13,Ffor stabbing to death university
OL,14,Fstudents Barnaby Webber and Grace
OL,15,FO'Malley-Kumar, both 19, as well as
OL,16,Fschool caretaker Ian Coates, 65, in
OL,17,Fthe early hours of June 13 2023.
