OL,6,FCalocane admitted manslaughter by
OL,7,Fdiminished responsibility and pleaded
OL,8,Fguilty to the attempted murder of
OL,9,Fthree people who were hit by a van
OL,10,Fstolen from Mr Coates, after
OL,11,FNottingham Crown Court heard he had
OL,12,Fbeen diagnosed with paranoid
OL,13,Fschizophrenia.
OL,15,FDuring a meeting with the Prime
OL,16,FMinister in February this year, the
OL,17,Ffamilies of the Nottingham attack
OL,18,Fvictims were told a judge-led
OL,19,Fstatutory inquiry would take place and
OL,20,Fthat it would scrutinise a "number of
OL,21,Fdifferent agencies".
